# =============================================================================
# Terraform
# =============================================================================
## Local state (never commit — use remote state instead)
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfstate.backup

## Crash log
crash.log
crash.*.log

## Override files
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json

## CLI config files
.terraformrc
terraform.rc

## Provider plugins and lock file (re-downloaded by terraform init)
.terraform/
.terraform.lock.hcl

## Sensitive variable files (use example files instead)
terraform.tfvars
*.auto.tfvars

## Plan files
*.tfplan

